Please note that we will not collect more than €50 M 
net, excluding all IGNIS crowdsale related commis-
sions, marketing, legal and organizational expenses. 

If we reach €50 M: 50% of any remaining unsold IGNIS 
(excluding the 60 M IGNIS already reserved for Jeluri-
da) will be distributed proportionally to all other IGNIS 
holders at the time of the Ardor Genesis Snapshot 
including both IGNIS crowdsale participants and NXT 
holders, the other 50% of the unsold IGNIS being kept 
byJelurida.

If the amount collected exceeds €50 M we will not 
conduct the remaining batches of the sales schedule, 
however any NXT already collected in excess of the 40 
M NXT reserved for Jelurida will still be sold.

If we do not reach €50 M, Jelurida will keep all 
remaining unsold IGNIS.

